The paper proposes a new algorithm for k-nearest neighbour search that is efficient in terms of time and space complexity, and allows for dynamic updates to the dataset. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to data structures (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
